{
  "stem": "21437.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But a little while later, we-- if I may, I will describe two incidents that might not give you answer to your question, but might illustrate certain things that happened in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The first was, when we moved to this street-- now, it was, I think, [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] G-O, Maja, M-A-J-A.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it could have been.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I am not sure 100%.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we lived, again, on the-- we lived on the first floor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was a small flat, but we had the whole little flat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "From the kitchen there was a delightful little balcony.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there is-- as a matter of fact, I think there is one lady here in Melbourne that lived there as well.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was going to my lesson, as always.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "By that time I was wearing already a white band with a Star of David that had to be visible at all times.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now there were certain streets, certain sides, that we were not allowed to walk, because the guards-- the German guards, the SS, the Wehrmacht or the Gestapo, whatever happened that they were in this particular time-- at this particular town, at this time, happened to walk to go to their quarters.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They had their quarters there, not far, really, from the boundaries that we had.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was walking from the lesson.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was elated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I remember I was running late, and I couldn't wait to share it with my mother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And apparently, when I walk, walked energetically, somehow I swung my arms.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the Star of David was not visible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now, I was very hungry at that stage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was very hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't remember if I had breakfast, if I had something or other.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I just don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
